LICENSE ← license file (placeholder or chosen license)
.gitignore ← ignore build artifacts, node_modules, secrets
CHANGELOG.md ← record major changes when you update policies
SECURITY.md ← how to report security/abuse issues
CONTRIBUTING.md ← how to contribute or propose doc edits
docs/
