Why this structure

docs/ is the canonical place for all textual governance, onboarding, and developer guides (searchable, easier to publish).
assets/ separates source design files from production exports and includes meta/ownership info.
scripts/ contains reproducible build steps (PDF export, assets optimization).
top-level files (README, CONTRIBUTING, SECURITY) give newcomers clear onboarding and safe-reporting paths.